data.description: Sellers are offering up to $5,000 toward title (Waypoint Title LLC). Conveniently located between FWB and Navarre, in Parish Point, this beautiful four-bedroom home has a lot of living space, a large driveway, a two car garage, and a well-kept yard with sprinkler system. The first floor includes tile flooring throughout and a large kitchen area. You'll also find the master bedroom along with a second bedroom. The living room offers a wood-burning fireplace, as well as a bonus room inside the entry that could be used as an office, playroom, or workout room. Upstairs you'll find a big loft/ open area before finding 2 more bedrooms and a full bathroom. Backyard is surrounded by solar lights and a sturdy workshop shed that is complete with electricity and new hardy board. Come on home!
